-- Saint Laurent Names Hedi Slimane Creative Director
-- B y   M a r t h e   F o u r c a d e
-- 2012-03-07T08:20:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-07/saint-laurent-names-hedi-slimane-creative-director-correct-.html
(Corrects designer’s first name in headline)  Yves Saint Laurent , the French
fashion house owned by  PPR (PP)  SA, appointed Hedi Slimane, who
designed its menswear collection until 2000, as creative
director. Slimane will have “total creative responsibility for
the brand image and all its collections,” PPR said in an e-
mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Marthe Fourcade at 
 mfourcade@bloomberg.net  